<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/876532-i-am-confused-i-know-that-the-initial">I am confused.....I know that the initial premise of a trade of 1000 white women for 1000 horses was turned down by President Roosevelt. But did the &#39;Brides for Indians&#39; program really occur? Did scores of women volunteer for this program?</a>
</div>
